{"no":94,"name":"سُورَةُ الشَّرۡحِ","enName":"Ash-Sharh","enNameTranslation":"The Consolation","bnNameTranslation":"আলাম নাশরাহ","revelationType":"Meccan","numberOfAyahs":8,"verses":[{"text":"أَلَمْ نَشْرَحْ لَكَ صَدْرَكَ","bnText":"আমি কি আপনার বক্ষ উম্মুক্ত করে দেইনি","enText":"Did We not expand for you, [O Muhammad], your breast?","enTextTransliteration":"Alam nashrah laka sadrak","audioPrimary":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6091","numberInSurah":1},{"text":"وَوَضَعْنَا عَنكَ وِزْرَكَ","bnText":"আমি লাঘব করেছি আপনার বোঝা","enText":"And We removed from you your burden","enTextTransliteration":"Wa wa d'ana 'anka wizrak","audioPrimary":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6092","numberInSurah":2},{"text":"الَّذِي أَنقَضَ ظَهْرَكَ","bnText":"যা ছিল আপনার জন্যে অতিশয় দুঃসহ।","enText":"Which had weighed upon your back","enTextTransliteration":"Allazee anqada zahrak","audioPrimary":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6093","numberInSurah":3},{"text":"وَرَفَعْنَا لَكَ ذِكْرَكَ","bnText":"আমি আপনার আলোচনাকে সমুচ্চ করেছি।","enText":"And raised high for you your repute.","enTextTransliteration":"Wa raf 'ana laka zikrak","audioPrimary":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6094","numberInSurah":4},{"text":"فَإِنَّ مَعَ الْعُسْرِ يُسْرًا","bnText":"নিশ্চয় কষ্টের সাথে স্বস্তি রয়েছে।","enText":"For indeed, with hardship [will be] ease.","enTextTransliteration":"Fa inna ma'al usri yusra","audioPrimary":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6095","numberInSurah":5},{"text":"إِنَّ مَعَ الْعُسْرِ يُسْرًا","bnText":"নিশ্চয় কষ্টের সাথে স্বস্তি রয়েছে।","enText":"Indeed, with hardship [will be] ease.","enTextTransliteration":"Inna ma'al 'usri yusra","audioPrimary":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/6096","numberInSurah":6},{"text":"فَإِذَا فَرَغْتَ فَانصَبْ","bnText":"অতএব, যখন অবসর পান পরিশ্রম করুন।","enText":"So when you have finished [your duties], then stand up [for